text: Tatyana Zharganova (born 24 July 1980) is a Belarusian gymnast. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Grodno
